### Get all user preferences
GET {{BASE_URL}}/user-preferences

### Get a single user preference by ID
GET {{BASE_URL}}/user-preferences/1

### Create a new user preference
POST {{BASE_URL}}/user-preferences
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "theme": "dark",
  "notifications": true
}

### Update a user preference by ID
PUT {{BASE_URL}}/user-preferences/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "theme": "light"
}

### Delete a user preference by ID
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/user-preferences/1
